{
  "text": "Here we should infer that \u03a3 \u221e P \u221e + \u2227KGL and KGL are stably cellular motivic ring spectra, a.k.a. \"Tate spectra\" [CITATION_1] . To begin with, the motivic K-theory spectrum KGL is stably cellular [CITATION_2] Theorem 6.2] . The suspension spectrum of the pointed infinite projective space is also stably cellular by [ ",
